&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;HR APPRENTICESHIP – WYE VALLEY NHS TRUST&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are offering a fantastic apprenticeship opportunity within our HR Business Partnering Team. Are you interested in a career in Human Resources? This might be the first step you are looking for; learning on the job and getting practical experience in an HR setting.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the HR apprentice you will be working in the heart of a busy and professional HR generalist service and will be the first point of contact for any general HR queries, maintain and update HR Systems, the collection and reporting of data while providing an efficient HR administrative services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an amazing opportunity to learn and develop a variety of HR skills, while studying for your Human Resources Apprenticeship, providing the beginnings of a long-term career path in HR. The apprenticeship will be of a period of 18 months.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you want to work in a fast paced environment where no two days are the same and where you can support an outstanding HR team to we would like to hear from YOU!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Jane Hanford, Head of HR email:jane.hanford@wvt.nhs.uk or &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Eleanor Jackson HRBP email: eleanor.jackson@wvt.nhs.uk&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
